snippet.title: Worms 4 - Android Gameplay
snippet.description:
No, this is not a mobile port of Worms 4: Mayhem. Instead, it's a different Worms game that focuses on the battle between the two factions. Each worm on your own team can be individually customized, while we also see weapons never seen outside this mobile outing.

Worms 4 © Team17 
Also released on iOS
